c: 3
v: 119
t: "Eneneni! Nini abathanda bona kodwa bona abanithandi, Ukanti nina nikholwa kuso sonke isiBhalo. Bona xa bedibana nani bathi, “Siyakholwa”. Kodwa xa behlangene bodwa, banimuncela iintupha zabo, bezele ngumsindo. Yithi: “Tshabalalani kuloo misindo yenu.” Inene uAllâh Uyakwazi oko kusezifubeni"